                  </hi> Wall—between May and September we had a large Quantity of woollen goods consigned to us from manufacturers to the order Of Learoyd, Wilton, and Co., and from time to time we have received transfer Orders in favour of Allen, Cauchai, Dunckley, Faulkner, and James, and Some for consiguments to Paris—we have some goods now belonging to the Firm; I have no 100<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; it might be over 200<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.</p>
