               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. GRAIN</hi>. Ours is a well-known firm, doing a large business—we are packers to the Government, and have been for 17 years—we receive a great number of woollen goods apecially for packing and ship<lb></lb>ment to various foreign parts—many of these goods were repacked and sent to Paris.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18800112-name-267" type="witnessName">
